Inventory Dashboard Overview 6

    5.0   Inventory Dashboard Overview

    Inventory Dashboard consists of three Worksheets:  

  • Total Weeks, Burned Weeks, Available Weeks and Booked Weeks Over the Years 
  • Avg Book to Stay and 
  • % Booked Weeks in Future

Inventory Dashboard - Drill Down Functionalities 6

 5.1  Drill Down Functionalities 
     Three Drill Down Functionalities are provided to users where they are able to drill down by

  • Property Status
  • Region and 
  • Filter by Date


    5    .1.1 Drill Down by Property Status 
     Property Status Drill Down Functionality has three options to choose in order to visualize the Data:
  • All
  • Standard
  • VIP

    5    .1.2   Drill Down by Region 
    Drill Down by Region Functionality provides the option to choose specific Region like:
  • Caribbean 
  • Central America
  • Gulf Cost and Florida, etc.


  • 5.1.3   Drill Down by Date
    Drill Down by Date Functionality provides the option to choose specific Month and Date to look into the Data
